query:
SELECT 
  id,
  task_id,
  highlight_id,
  status,
  created_at
FROM avatar_video_tasks
WHERE created_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL 5 MINUTE
ORDER BY created_at DESC
LIMIT 5;
